- source_id=pg_005:rotated_scope:f11 fragment_id=f11 cost=2 text="Read your assigned plan's `PLAN.md`. It carries the plan-critic's `<review>` block. Read that feedback and revise the plan's `PLAN.md` in place to address every point raised. Preserve the two-part structure (formalized model plus chosen solving strategy). Don't discard the plan and start over, and don't leave a flagged issue unaddressed. You revise; you do not create new plans. Do not read or touch other plans' files."
